{"tid":2083311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全國人大常委會開會　沈春耀報告港區國安法審議結果   相信草案已列入表決議程","createTime":"2020-06-28T15:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T00:23:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0e5538b6a34b375a3e789ecca069532cfff07a","tid":2083311,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534580-20200628.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534580-20200628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=0e912a1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534580-20200628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a2ca06fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534580-20200628.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會今日起一連三日在北京人民大會堂召開會議。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，會議聽取了全國人大憲法和法律委員會副主任沈春耀，就「港區國安法」草案審議結果的報告，但未有透露條文內容。央視報道指，在早上舉行的分組會議上，與會人士認為有關內容提出的具體措施更針對性及具可操作性。<br />\n<br />\n有列席會議的港區人大透露，草案有部分內容修改，相信草案已列入表決議程。"},{"pid":"7ecf45920006276180fcf18fa599c018b13c97fd","tid":2083311,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"不如<br />\n大家等佢通過咗先開呢啲post"},{"pid":"0e4e70a3f1732baba0671bf321586b776a0e2fc7","tid":2083311,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"快啦，好悶"},{"pid":"c910abdbf8222cf534a891460e902fa2bde20d70","tid":2083311,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"係表決就表決, 一日十鳩幾廿個新聞講就表就表係做乜春, 想嚇我啊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515913ac4e65c540dd64f262c55c12f06a8a0263","tid":2083311,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:12:45.000Z","msg":"有就有冇就冇啦<br />\n相信咩鳩啊<img src=\"/assets